<lg met="sragdharā : - - - - ⏑ - - / ⏑ ⏑ ⏑ ⏑ ⏑ ⏑ - / - ⏑ - - ⏑ - -">
<lb n="1"/><l n="a">āvirbhūte śakendre vasudahanarasai<choice><sic>r</sic><corr>ḥ</corr><corr>x</corr></choice> kāmin<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>ī</corr></choice>madhyacandre</l>
<l n="b">siṁhe lagne tulāyāṁ dinakaratanaye ghāṭike jīvaśukre</l>
<lb n="2"/><l n="c">m<choice><sic>i</sic><corr>ī</corr></choice>nendrendvātmajāte kṣitisutasahite bhūritīkṣṇāṅśujāle</l>
<l n="d">devaś śrīpuṣkareśo dvijavaramunibhis sthāpitaḥ puṣkareṇa</l>
</lg>
